{"tid":2135631,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"九龍城法院再多一名保安員確診 律師批不關庭憂現「法庭群組」","createTime":"2020-08-01T14:23:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T14:25:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"27b675307ecc720da21b206f6ed5a30aea853af3","tid":2135631,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:23:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200801/VMGE75ZRZ4ZAS2ECOW2MOWBQ7U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200801%2FVMGE75ZRZ4ZAS2ECOW2MOWBQ7U%2F&d=e0fscszCypj9zTmdFU62PuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=2be56e1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200801%2FVMGE75ZRZ4ZAS2ECOW2MOWBQ7U%2F&h=0a6f47f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200801/VMGE75ZRZ4ZAS2ECOW2MOWBQ7U/</a><br />\n<br />\n九龍城法院接連出現保安人員出現武漢肺炎確診個案。前日司法機構表示有保安確診武漢肺炎，今日（8月1日）保安主管亦同樣確診病毒。司法機構回覆《蘋果》查詢指，會立即為法庭進行清潔消毒，與患者密切接觸人士已被通知接受隔離及檢驗，卻沒有提及會否暫時關閉法院。有律師批評司法機構堅持照開庭，做法不負責任。"},{"pid":"0d0e5b747a2cefd3d14c052532a36271d9b9dbe4","tid":2135631,"uid":132587,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:26:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0cae20dcfa4c4de75271249cc4257bdd7de39d9b","tid":2135631,"uid":63287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"你同保安會近距離唔戴口罩接觸？"},{"pid":"29680670d46e0408dca4139e729a9650559f4930","tid":2135631,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:33:15.000Z","msg":"九龍城法院有咩狗官<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04526208d3ca0d096cd907752d787fb23e1b240","tid":2135631,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hk